\sum_{m=k}^\infty p_m > 0
     \mathbb{E}\left(T_k\right) - k = \underbrace{\sum_{m=0}^{k-1} m p_m + \left(\mathbb{E}\left(T_k\right) -k\right) \sum_{m=0}^{k-1} p_m}_{ \text{transition to } m < k} + \underbrace{\sum_{m=k}^\infty (m-k) p_m}_{\text{transition to } m\geqslant k} 
     \mathbb{E}\left(T_k\right) \left(1-\sum_{m=0}^{k-1} p_m\right) = \sum_{m=0}^\infty m p_m \qquad \therefore  \quad  \mathbb{E}\left(T_k\right) = \frac{\sum_{m=0}^\infty m p_m}{\sum_{m=k}^\infty  p_m} 
